001
002package com.commercetools.api.models.order;
003
004import java.util.List;
005
006import com.commercetools.api.models.type.CustomFields;
007
008public interface ParcelMixin {
009    public ParcelMeasurements getMeasurements();
010
011    public TrackingData getTrackingData();
012
013    public List<DeliveryItem> getItems();
014
015    public CustomFields getCustom();
016
017    public default ParcelDraftBuilder toDraftBuilder() {
018        return ParcelDraft.builder()
019                .measurements(this.getMeasurements())
020                .trackingData(this.getTrackingData())
021                .items(this.getItems())
022                .custom(this.getCustom().toDraft());
023    }
024
025    public default ParcelDraft toDraft() {
026        return toDraftBuilder().build();
027    }
028}
